<br>
1) A Ntov Guild wont go into NTov until full spawn<br>
2) A full spawn can take more than 48hrs in some instances.<br>
3) Eash and Ik can spawn before ALL mobs in Ntov are up.<br>
4) NTov guild will have a pretty good idea when their up and when mobs are due to spawn.<br>
5) Aary currently must be killed before your on NTov Rotation.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
So maybe it should go something like this?<br>
<br>
<br>
1) You cannot kill Ik and/or Eash if Aary and Feshak are not up. (to try to avoid the slow respawns in Ntov)  Maybe even add Vyemm to that list of must be up.<br>
<br>
2) Every other of your attempts at Ik and Eash you MUST attempt Aary.<br>
<br>
3) You cannot kill Ik and/or Eash more than once consecutively. You must &quot;wait&quot; 1 spawn before you can try again. <br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
This should stop Farmers / snipers but still give the Ntov guilds SOME spawns on Ik and Eash but not exclusive it will also give the smaller guilds a go at Ik and Eash.<br>
